{"tid":2452744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"無懼死亡個案 市民續打科興：美國疫苗都有不良反應","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:34:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"72a0395063d86fa3134bb2a0ac0a96f057ff8f86","tid":2452744,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"從事金融業的林先生是年輕的接種一族，他因需要到中國出差，故預約今日先接種科興疫苗。他稱對中國疫苗有信心，認為中國始終為首個發現武漢肺炎的地方，所以研究時間會相對長。而接種疫苗前林先生亦有做相關研究，他指每隻疫苗都有不良反應，美國疫苗亦皆是。林先生解釋輝瑞為mRNA疫苗，正開發用作治療癌症，因此用作傳染病疫苗是「對全人類的最新體驗」，所以他表示對傳統的滅活疫苗較有信心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3qVWt9rPKt8nYbRLTvY9_3zqLdA=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D4N457US6NCC3M4SMODBNTF3CM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3qVWt9rPKt8nYbRLTvY9_3zqLdA%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD4N457US6NCC3M4SMODBNTF3CM.JPG&h=1c8a104f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林先生<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210319/3ZKBAY5IBNC77E7WHAV5KB3PW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210319%2F3ZKBAY5IBNC77E7WHAV5KB3PW4%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=a14c557f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210319%2F3ZKBAY5IBNC77E7WHAV5KB3PW4%2F&h=a2cc1fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210319/3ZKBAY5IBNC77E7WHAV5KB3PW4/</a>"},{"pid":"2a4ff225415f7134840dacbc2536307f1dc5e796","tid":2452744,"uid":174060,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osAX7NT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosAX7NT.gif&h=c5b36513&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tk3ZBGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k